naked at DESC’s clothing sort in Columbia City on
Thursday, March 10 at 5:30pm, bury the dead at
Calvary Cemetery by U Village on Saturday,
March 19, 9:30am, and feed the hungry at St.
Mary’s Food bank on Saturday, March 26 at 9am.
E-mail Tom for more details or to RSVP.</p>
