<p><b>MAKE YOUR MARRIAGE A PRIORITY THIS LENTEN
SEASON</b>. It’s not too late to focus on something
positive during Lent: making your marriage everything
God intended it to be. Retrouvaille (pronounced retrov&#299;)
can help you rediscover your spouse and move
forward in a more positive and loving way. The next
program starts April 8, 2016. Confidential <i>information
and registration</i>, 360-671-6479 or
<a target="_bulletin" href="http://www.HelpOurMarriage.com">www.HelpOurMarriage.com</a>.</p>
