integrate faith into everyday life. All are welcome!</p>
<p><b>SPECIAL NEEDS MASS & DANCE</b> Saturday, March
12. Join us as we help to host the annual Mass for
people with special needs followed immediately by
a dance in the O’Dea gym. We are seeking youth
volunteers to run the event. Please contact Joe to
volunteer.</p>
<p><b>LENTEN YOUTH RETREAT</b> March 19-20. Join us
for an overnight retreat experience here on
campus. The theme is: Preparation for the Passion,
Death, and Resurrection. To register, contact Joe.</p>
